x-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><div style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px;"><br></div></div><div style="box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><div style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px;"><div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="4823" data-elementor-settings="[]" style="box-sizing: inherit; hyphens: manual;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section data-id="3a4a538" data-element_type="section" style="box-sizing: border-box; display: block; position: relative;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; position: relative; max-width: 100%;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1160px; display: flex;"><div data-id="b12e115" data-element_type="column" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; display: flex; width: 1160px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; width: 1160px; position: relative; display: flex; padding: 0px 10px 10px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; width: 1140px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-content: flex-start; display: flex;"><div data-id="7c752be" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; color: rgb(122, 122, 122); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; width: 1140px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; transition: background 0.3s ease 0s, border 0.3s ease 0s, border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">O&lsquo;zbekistonda ta&rsquo;lim sohasi, xususan, maktab ta&rsquo;limi tizimida keng ko&lsquo;lamli islohotlarni amalga oshirish rejalashtirilmoqda. Bunda quyidagi xalqaro standartlar va talablarga javob beradigan umumta&rsquo;lim maktablari bitiruvchilarini tayyorlash rejalashtirilmoqda:</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">&bull; zamonaviy malaka;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">&bull; axborot texnologiyalarini mukammal egallash;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">&bull; ijodiy fikrlash;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">&bull; mustaqil ravishda qaror qabul qilish;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">&bull; keng dunyoqarashga ega bo&lsquo;lish.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Ushbu yo&lsquo;nalishning dolzarbligi nimada?</strong></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Jahon amaliyoti shuni ko&lsquo;rsatadiki, insonning muvaffaqiyatli faoliyati, qolaversa, butun jamiyatning farovonlik sari harakatlanishi kafolati bu&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">zamonaviy sifatlar va malakaga ega bo&lsquo;lishdir.</strong> Shu bilan birga, jadal rivojlanayotgan iqtisodiyotda ish beruvchining talablarini qondirish tobora qiyinlashib bormoqda. Masalan, O&lsquo;zbekistondagi ish beruvchilar eng avvalo, bo&lsquo;lg&lsquo;usi xodimlardan ijodiy fikrlash, mustaqil qaror qabul qilish, keng dunyoqarash kabi universal (ijtimoiy) ko&lsquo;nikmalarga ega bo&lsquo;lishni talab qiladi. Bu esa, o&lsquo;z navbatida, kadrlarning doimiy ravishda kasbiy malakasini oshirish, bilimlarini boyitish, shuningdek, shaxsning jamiyatda muloqot qilish qobiliyatini o&lsquo;stirishni taqozo etadi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Garvard va Yel</strong> universiteti, Iqtisodiy tadqiqotlar milliy byurosi iqtisodchilari&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">D.Deming</strong> va&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">L.Kan</strong> (2017), 2010-2015 yillardagi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">BGT</strong> ma&#39;lumotlariga asoslanib, malakalarga bo&rsquo;lgan talabning o&lsquo;zgarishini o&lsquo;rgandi. Ular kalit&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">so&#39;zlardan</strong> foydalanib,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">o&#39;nta guruhdan</strong> iborat malaka tasnifini taklif qildi. Ushbu tasniflagich turli sohalarda talab qilinadigan shaxsiy va ijtimoiy malakani, shuningdek, har bir kasb uchun alohida talab qilinadigan kasbiy malakani o&#39;z ichiga oladi. Ular ko&lsquo;nikmalarning o&lsquo;zaro bir-birini to&lsquo;ldirishi, ijtimoiy malakaning roli ortib borayotgani, korxonalarning oylik maoshlar va yaxshi natijaga erishishida malakaning sezilarli kuchga ega ekanligini aniqladi. Ular o&#39;z tadqiqotida yuqori maoshli mehnat bozorlari va firmalar o&#39;z xodimlaridan yuqori darajadagi kognitiv va ijtimoiy ko&#39;nikmalarni talab qilishini isbotladi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">PMTI ekspertlari</strong> O&lsquo;zbekistondagi ish beruvchilar orasida eng ko&lsquo;p talab qilinadigan ko&rsquo;nikmalarni aniqlash bo&lsquo;yicha tadqiqot o&lsquo;tkazdi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">O&lsquo;zbekiston mehnat bozorida talab yuqori bo&lsquo;lgan malakani aniqlash uchun&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">PMTI</strong> mutaxassislari mavjud bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlari ma&rsquo;lumotlar bazasini o&lsquo;rgandi.&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Head</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Hunter</strong> (www.hh.uz),&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Bandlik va mehnat munosabatlari vazirligining bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlari&nbsp;</strong>(www.mehnat.uz),&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Olx job</strong> (www.olx.uz) va boshqalar ularning orasida eng taniqlilaridir. Aytib o&rsquo;tish joizki, bitta &nbsp;vakansiya bir vaqtning o&#39;zida turli saytlarda e&#39;lon qilinishi mumkin.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Ushbu tadqiqotda&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">PMTI</strong> mutaxassislari&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Head Hunter&nbsp;</strong>ma&#39;lumotlar bazasidan foydalandi. Mazkur maʼlumotlar bazasida Oʻzbekistonning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">12 mingga</strong> yaqin kompaniyasi va ish qidiruvchilarning<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;370 mingga</strong> yaqin rezyumesi roʻyxatga olingan. Bu esa ish beruvchilar va ish qidiruvchilar tomonidan unga boʻlgan ishonchdan dalolat beradi. O&#39;rganish vaqtida ma&#39;lumotlar bazasida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">4 mingdan</strong> ortiq bo&#39;sh ish o&#39;rinlari qayd etildi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">Ma&rsquo;lumot uchun:</em></strong><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">&nbsp;Linkedin kompaniyasi tadqiqotlari shuni ko&lsquo;rsatdiki</em><a href="https://imrs.uz/publications/articles-and-abstracts/skills#_ftn1" name="_ftnref1" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; box-shadow: none;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">[1]</strong></em></strong></a><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">,&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">2022 yilda</strong> Soft skills (moslashuvchan ko&rsquo;nikmalar) jahon mehnat bozorida xodimni yollash to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida qaror qabul qilishda muhim mezonga aylandi. Ushbu tadqiqot natijalariga ko&#39;ra, ijodkorlik, o&#39;ziga ishonch, jamoada ishlash va moslashuvchanlik eng ko&#39;p talab qilinadigan ko&lsquo;nikmalar bo&lsquo;lgan.</em></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">Dunyoda&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">50 mingdan</strong> ortiq ko&#39;nikma mavjud bo&#39;lib, ular asosan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ikki turga</strong> bo&#39;linadi: &quot;qattiq&quot; (Hard skills) va &quot;moslashuvchan&quot; (Soft skills). Qattiq ko&#39;nikmalar - bu biz topshiriqni bajarishda tajribaga ega bo&#39;lgan kas mahoratidir. Bu o&#39;zlashtirilgan kompyuter dasturi, dasturlash tili, chet tili va boshqalar bo&#39;lishi mumkin. Yumshoq yoki universal ko&#39;nikmalar - bu ish jarayonida yordam beradigan xodimning ixtisoslashmagan fazilatlari. Masalan, kommunikativ qobiliyat, ijodkorlik, jamoada ishlash qobiliyati va h.k. Shuni ta&#39;kidlash kerakki, so&#39;nggi yillarda Moslashuvchan ko&rsquo;nikmalar ish beruvchilar orasida ko&#39;proq talab qilinmoqda.</em></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">PMTI ekspertlari</strong> Head Hunter saytida taqdim etilgan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">3384&nbsp;</strong>ta bo&#39;sh ish o&#39;rnini tahlil qildi. Bunda faqat kerakli ko&#39;nikmalar va ish haqi ko&#39;rsatilgan bo&#39;sh ish o&#39;rinlari o&rsquo;rganildi. Ma&rsquo;lum bo&lsquo;lishicha, har bir bo&#39;sh ish o&#39;rniga oʻrtacha&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">4,2 ta</strong> malaka toʻgʻri kelar ekan. Ko&#39;nikmalar soni o&#39;ntagacha yetishi mumkin, ammo bo&lsquo;lg&lsquo;usi xodim uchun bir vaqtning o&#39;zida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">4 yoki 5&nbsp;</strong>ta ko&rsquo;nikmaga ega bo&#39;lish kifoya. Ko&#39;nikmalar tasnifini shakllantirishda yuqorida aytib o&#39;tilgan&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Deming va Kanning</strong> o&#39;n guruhli sxemasidan foydalanildi. Shuningdek, ushbu tasniflagichga chet tillarini bilish ko&#39;nikmasi qo&#39;shildi.</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">Tahlil davomida quyidagilar ma&#39;lum bo&#39;ldi:</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlarining&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">86</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">%</strong> ida ish qidiruvchilardan kamida bir yillik ish stajiga ega bo&lsquo;lish talab qilinadi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlarining&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">11,3</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">%</strong> ida oliy ma&rsquo;lumotga ega bo&lsquo;lish talab etiladi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- bo&#39;sh ish o&#39;rinlarining&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">28%</strong> ida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">ijtimoiy ko&#39;nikmalarni</strong> ya&rsquo;ni, jamoada ishlash, muzokaralar olib borish, malakali nutq, muloqot, omma oldida taqdimot qilish qobiliyatlari talab etilishi ma&rsquo;lum bo&rsquo;ldi;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- vakansiyalarning &nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">18,3%</strong> ida chet tillarini (asosan ingliz tili) bilish talabi ko&rsquo;rsatilgan;</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;">- vakansiyalarning&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">15,2%</strong> ida&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">shaxsiy ko&lsquo;nikmalar</strong>, ya&rsquo;ni mas&rsquo;uliyat, stressga chidamlilik, ijodkorlik, motivatsiya, yetakchilik fazilatlari talab etilmoqda,&nbsp;<em style="box-sizing: border-box; font-style: italic;">shuningdek,</em> <strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">kompyuter savodxonligi</strong> ham eng ko&rsquo;p talab qilinuvchi ko&rsquo;nikma ekanligi ma&rsquo;lum bo&lsquo;ldi (bo&lsquo;sh ish o&lsquo;rinlarining 12,5% ida so&rsquo;ralgan) (1-rasm)</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: right;">1-rasm</h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: center;"><img src="https://imrs.uz/public/ckfinder/userfiles/files/image(232).png" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: none; height: 616px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; width: 974px;" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></h3><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; clear: both; text-align: justify;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">Head Hunter&nbsp;</strong>saytida taqdim etilgan bo&#39;sh ish o&#39;rinlarini tahlil qilish jarayonida O&lsquo;zbekiston mehnat bozorida talab yuqori bo&lsquo;lgan mutaxassisliklar aniqlandi. &nbsp;Bugungi kunda barcha turdagi&nbsp;<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;">menejerlarga talab yuqori ekanligi ma&rsquo;lum bo&rsquo;ldi</strong>, xususan, savdo (bo&#39;sh ish o&#39;rinlarining 30% dan ko&#39;prog&#39;i), xizmat ko&#39;rsatish sohasida (mehmonxonalar, restoranlar, go&#39;zallik salonlari va xu